channel.title: A Continuation of TheHolyGrail's F2P Remake
channel.description:
Hi.
I'm going to be re creating TheHolyGrail's F2P Remake. Although, it will have a lot more features. In no way will it be complete, but it will be a start for noobs. I'm at school right now, so I can't post pictures or make a project thread, but it will be done soon.
